  <h4 class="teaser-headline">
      <a href="/article/what-is-a-photon?language_content_entity=und" rel="bookmark"><span>What is a photon?</span>
</a>
  </h4> 
  <p>The fundamental particle of light is both ordinary and full of surprises.</p>


